These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 10

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, fanta, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, photography, singing, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, blues, indie, pop
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 2. the person drinking coffee is not to the left of the person drinking fanta##8
 3. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the fan pop##3
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is not the fan blues##6
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is the person drinking fanta or the person who's hobby is singing is the fan indie, but not both##10
 6. the person drinking fanta and the fan ambient have the same parity positions##9
 7. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the fan indie##3
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the fan pop##5
 9. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person drinking coffee and the fan ambient##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta   | sprite      | coffee    |
| Hobby         | drawing     | singing | photography | skydiving |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | ambient | pop         | blues     |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-2::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, peach, peas, raspberry
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, french, italian, spanish
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, horse, snake
 1. the egyptian is the person eating raspberry or the owner of the snake is the egyptian, but not both##10
 2. the italian is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
 3. the egyptian is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3
 4. the owner of the horse and the egyptian have different parity positions##9
 5. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 6. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
 7. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the italian##3
 8. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
 9. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating peach##1
10. the owner of the fish is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
11. the spanish is in an even position##4
12. the egyptian is the person eating lettuce or the egyptian is the owner of the snake, but not both##10
13. the person eating lettuce is not to the right of the person eating peas##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | peach    | lettuce | peas    |
| Nationality   | italian   | egyptian | french  | spanish |
| Pet           | horse     | snake    | fish    | frog    |

