.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, sprite, tea
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, grapefruit, lime, onion
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, japanese, spanish, thai
1. the person eating onion is the italian##1
2. the person eating lime is on the far right##1
3. the person eating onion is the thai or the person eating onion is the person drinking hot-chocolate, but not both##10
4. the person eating lime is not to the right of the person drinking coffee##8
5. the spanish is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
6. the japanese is between the person eating cauliflower and the italian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage      | tea         | sprite     | hot-chocolate | coffee |
| Food          | cauliflower | grapefruit | onion         | lime   |
| Nationality   | spanish     | japanese   | italian       | thai   |

