.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-4::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, cabbage, grapes, pineapple
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, cooking, fishing, writing
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, canadian, chinese, polish
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the canadian##1
 2. the australian is not to the right of the person eating grapes##8
 3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
 4. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is not the australian##6
 6. the canadian is somewhere to the left of the person eating cabbage##5
 7. the person who's hobby is writing is the chinese or the person who's hobby is writing is the person eating cabbage, but not both##10
 8. the chinese is the person eating grapes or the chinese is the person who's hobby is cooking, but not both##10
 9. the polish is somewhere between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person eating grapes##7
10. the polish is on the right of the person eating banana##1
11. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | pineapple  | banana   | cabbage | grapes  |
| Hobby         | baking     | fishing  | cooking | writing |
| Nationality   | australian | canadian | polish  | chinese |

