.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, juice, soy-milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, crime, horror, musical
4 different pets are kept: cat, hedgehog, mouse, rabbit
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the cat is not the person watching crime movies##6
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person watching horror movies and the person watching action movies##2
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is not the person watching musical movies##6
 5. the owner of the rabbit and the person watching action movies have different parity positions##9
 6. the person drinking cola is the person watching action movies or the person drinking cola is the owner of the cat, but not both##10
 7. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
 8. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
10. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
11. the owner of the mouse is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person drinking soy-milk##7
12. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage      | cola   | soy-milk | iced-tea | juice   |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | crime    | action   | musical |
| Pet           | cat    | hedgehog | mouse    | rabbit  |

