.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, card-games, puzzles, singing
There are 4 different nationalities: american, chinese, dutch, nigerian
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, ship, train, trike
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##5
 2. the american is the person who's hobby is camping or the american is the person driving the trike, but not both##10
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##8
 4. the person driving the ship and the nigerian have different parity positions##9
 5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 6. the nigerian is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
 7. the chinese is on the far right##1
 8. the dutch is somewhere between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the american##7
 9. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
10. the nigerian is between the person driving the train and the dutch##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | camping   | card-games | puzzles  | singing |
| Nationality   | american  | dutch      | nigerian | chinese |
| Transport     | quad-bike | ship       | trike    | train   |

