.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-7::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, grapefruit, orange, potato
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, librarian, security-guard, teacher
4 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, dog, goldfish
 1. the person eating potato is not to the left of the person eating orange##8
 2. the analyst is between the owner of the bird and the person eating potato##2
 3. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the teacher##3
 4. the person eating potato is somewhere between the person eating grapefruit and the owner of the chinchilla##7
 5. the owner of the chinchilla and the person eating garlic have the same parity positions##9
 6. the librarian is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 7. the security-guard is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
 8. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
 9. the owner of the bird is the analyst or the owner of the bird is the person eating orange, but not both##10
10. the owner of the bird and the librarian have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |       3        |     4      |
| Food   | orange    | garlic     | potato         | grapefruit |
| Job    | librarian | analyst    | security-guard | teacher    |
| Pet    | bird      | chinchilla | dog            | goldfish   |

