The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, fishing, puzzles, video-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, romance, sports, thriller
 1. the person eating corn is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
 2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not to the right of the person watching romance movies##8
 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an even position##4
 5. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5
 6. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching thriller movies##5
 7. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 8. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapes##5
 9. the person eating pumpkin is not to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##8
10. the person watching romance movies is the person who's hobby is puzzles or the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person eating plum, but not both##10
11. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
