 6. the teacher is between the social-worker and the nurse##2
 7. the person driving the bus and the pilot have different parity positions##9
 8. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the right of the person watching thriller movies##5
 9. the person watching scientific movies is the person driving the bus or the person watching scientific movies is the teacher, but not both##10
10. the person driving the train and the person watching scientific movies have the same parity positions##9

