 1. the person drinking mirinda is not to the left of the person eating kiwi##8
 2. the owner of the frog is not to the right of the person eating papaya##8
 3. the owner of the goldfish is the person drinking mirinda or the owner of the goldfish is the person eating kiwi, but not both##10
 4. the person eating papaya is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
 5. the person eating spinach is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8
 6. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
 7. the person drinking juice is not to the left of the person eating lemon##8
 8. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
 9. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
10. the person eating papaya is the person drinking water or the person eating papaya is the owner of the goldfish, but not both##10
11. the owner of the hedgehog and the person eating kiwi have the same parity positions##9
12. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2   |    3     |    4     |
