 1. the person who's sport is climbing is not the person driving the boat##6
 2. the fan disco is not to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##8
 3. the fan disco is not to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##8
 4. the fan folk is the person who's sport is climbing or the person driving the bus is the fan folk, but not both##10
 5. the fan electronic is somewhere to the left of the fan folk##5
 6. the fan rock is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##8
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 9. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4
10. the fan disco is in an even position##4
11. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
12. the person driving the boat and the fan rock have the same parity positions##9
13. the fan disco is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3

.:: Answer ::.
