 7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
 8. the person eating grapes is the owner of the lizard##1
 9. the person watching drama movies is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8
10. the owner of the ferret is not the person watching epic movies##6
11. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
12. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
13. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
14. the person watching disaster movies is not to the left of the owner of the lizard##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |      4      |
| Food          | grapes   | cranberry | spinach  | lime        |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | epic      | drama    | documentary |
| Pet           | lizard   | rabbit    | hedgehog | ferret      |

